Title: Canopy
Author: Chris Hart
Version: 0.2
=Requirements=
	* Python < 2.6
	* 2 servers: localhost and firewallhost
	* Passwordless SSH from localhost -> firewallhost
		--> easy setup with ssh-keygen

=Installation=
	* All files go in localhost:/etc except canopy.rbl goes in firewallhost:/root
		--> Place files according to canopy.conf
	* /etc/canopy/canopy can be symlinked into init.d as required

